38:06.481 --> 38:08.506
Think about how I was feeling yesterday.

38:08.683 --> 38:10.708
- I know.
- I could've called in sick.

38:10.885 --> 38:12.080
I know.

38:12.887 --> 38:14.150
- Then what?
- Oh, my Lord.

38:15.256 --> 38:16.747
Shaw.

38:17.192 --> 38:18.557
- No, I gotta go.
- Doing okay?

38:19.361 --> 38:20.350
No.

38:21.363 --> 38:23.024
That bomb went off on my watch.

38:23.198 --> 38:24.563
That's my fucking park.

38:25.166 --> 38:28.500
We didn't have enough eyeballs there.
That's on us.

38:29.571 --> 38:31.164
Let's just catch
the son of a bitch, yeah?

38:31.740 --> 38:32.707
Yeah.

38:33.108 --> 38:35.167
I need you to get out
to Habersham County.

38:35.343 --> 38:36.834
Background on a former sheriffs deputy.

38:37.012 --> 38:38.570
Might have some connection
to the bombing.

38:39.080 --> 38:40.070
Who is it?

38:40.915 --> 38:42.406
The security guard.

38:55.063 --> 38:56.189
Hey, Richard!

39:00.802 --> 39:02.531
Hey, way to go, man.

39:02.604 --> 39:04.037
You made us all real proud.

39:06.041 --> 39:07.099
Thank you.

39:11.546 --> 39:15.312
Dr. Cleere, we wanna thank you
for contacting the FBI

39:15.383 --> 39:18.751
