Small Business Admin anymore?

42:35.416 --> 42:36.782
'Cause I tried there first

42:36.951 --> 42:38.317
No, I moved on.

42:38.620 --> 42:39.712
Oh. How come?

42:39.787 --> 42:41.517
Lifestyle decision.

42:42.090 --> 42:43.580
What's your phone number?

42:44.492 --> 42:46.187
My phone number is 404...

42:46.261 --> 42:47.091
404...

42:47.262 --> 42:49.457
- 194...
- 194...

42:49.631 --> 42:51.929
- 8188.
- 8188.

42:52.100 --> 42:54.500
All right, well,
you just don't sign anything

42:54.669 --> 42:57.138
until I see it first. We'll start there.

42:57.305 --> 42:58.363
Yes, sir.

42:58.539 --> 43:01.634
Yeah, I won't put a pen to the page.
I'll wait on it.

43:02.477 --> 43:04.968
Hey, and thank you, sir.
Thank you for your time.

43:05.146 --> 43:06.136
You got it

43:06.314 --> 43:07.440
All right, bye.

43:07.615 --> 43:08.844
- Stay in touch.
- Yes, sir.

43:09.017 --> 43:10.484
- Okay.
- Bye,

43:15.790 --> 43:16.951
No, no.

43:17.125 --> 43:19.685
Don't get too excited.

43:21.162 --> 43:22.527
- No.
- Yes.

43:22.697 --> 43:25.098
No. Simmer down there, hot sauce.

43:27.802 --> 43:29.827
Well, Bill Miller.

43:30.004 --> 43:32.405
It's nice to see you. It's been a while.

43:32.573 --> 43:34.041
It's nice to see you, Bobi.

43:34.208 --> 43:35.232
Where's the hero?

43:35.610 --> 43:37.635
Oh, he's in here. Come on in.

43:43.017 --> 43:44.951
What kind of charge
you figure it was?

43:45.019 --> 43:45.850
Mmm.

43:47.855 --> 43:50.552
I'm not sure what kind of explosive
