it blew upward.

44:17.251 --> 44:19.447
Most of the ordnance
going up into the sky.

44:20.388 --> 44:21.856
It blew up.

44:23.024 --> 44:25.618
So, all in all, what you're looking at
is some kind of battery,

44:25.693 --> 44:29.129
