45:42.470 --> 45:43.835
No more so than usual.

45:45.106 --> 45:46.665
Sure, just another... Thank you.

45:47.508 --> 45:51.468
Just your average deadly bombing
on US soil during the Olympics.

45:51.646 --> 45:52.875
No big deal.

45:54.382 --> 45:56.680
I don't know, you guys must be
feeling the heat, too, huh?

45:56.751 --> 45:57.581
Mmm-hmm.

45:58.319 --> 46:00.048
CNN is going wall-to-wall with this.

46:00.121 --> 46:01.782
