46:08.930 --> 46:10.796
Kathy, you know I can't do that.

46:11.999 --> 46:14.332
That's all right. I already know
the Bureau's looking into somebody.

46:14.402 --> 46:16.131
Yeah, what makes you think that?

46:17.004 --> 46:17.994
Friends.

46:18.172 --> 46:19.196
- Friends?
- Sources.

46:19.373 --> 46:20.397
Sources?

46:22.343 --> 46:23.640
Who is it?

46:25.546 --> 46:27.571
Well, Kathy, if you couldn't
fuck it out of them,

46:27.648 --> 46:29.742
what makes you think
you're gonna fuck it outta me?

46:33.754 --> 46:36.155
You know what bothers me, Kathy,
is that people don't understand

46:36.224 --> 46:38.124
how much work goes into
making a case like this.

46:38.192 --> 46:40.354
It's effort 24/7.

46:41.128 --> 46:41.959
Hmm.

46:42.430 --> 46:43.727
You're right

46:47.768 --> 46:49.498
Why don't you educate me?

46:51.672 --> 46:54.266
I will not have this screwed up.

46:54.442 --> 46:55.739
That was a massacre out there.

46:55.810 --> 46:57.278
It's a miracle
more people weren't killed.

46:57.445 --> 46:58.742
I would never go to print

46:58.813 --> 47:01.543
