in a very different zone.

47:07.021 --> 47:08.352
As you know.

47:10.591 --> 47:11.786
Really?

47:11.859 --> 47:12.917
Mmm-hmm.

47:13.728 --> 47:14.957
What kind of zone?

47:15.696 --> 47:17.130
You have to find out

47:30.945 --> 47:34.108
We're looking at
the security guard, Jewell.

47:37.585 --> 47:39.144
- No shit?
- No shit.

47:40.988 --> 47:42.649
You always look at the guy
who found the bomb,

47:42.723 --> 47:44.658
just like you always look at the guy
who found the body.

47:44.725 --> 47:47.524
But this guy, he's got a bad past.

47:48.429 --> 47:52.366
Fits the profile of
the hero-bomber to a T.

47:52.433 --> 47:56.131
That fat fuck who lives with his mother.
Of course.

47:56.604 --> 47:59.903
How did I miss that?
I mean, that is amazing.

48:00.775 --> 48:01.742
Ooh.

48:01.809 --> 48:03.174
You are good.

48:03.344 --> 48:04.743
You're very good.

48:04.912 --> 48:06.175
Yeah.

48:06.347 --> 48:08.247
This kind of puts a clock
on things, though.

48:08.316 --> 48:10.147
You wanna get a room
or just go to my car?

48:13.788 --> 48:14.812
This is happening.

48:14.989 --> 48:16.115
This is happening.

48:17.858 --> 48:18.917
Let's get the fuck outta here.

48:18.993 --> 48:19.983
- Okay.
